001package com.technototes.path.subsystem;
002
003import java.lang.annotation.Annotation;
004import java.lang.annotation.ElementType;
005import java.lang.annotation.Retention;
006import java.lang.annotation.RetentionPolicy;
007import java.lang.annotation.Target;
008import java.lang.reflect.Field;
009
010import com.acmerobotics.roadrunner.control.PIDCoefficients;
011import com.qualcomm.robotcore.hardware.PIDFCoefficients;
012
013@SuppressWarnings("unused")
014@FunctionalInterface
015public interface TankConstants {
016
017    Class getConstant();
018
019    default double getDouble(Class<? extends Annotation> a) {
020        for (Field f : getConstant().getFields()) {
021            try {
022                if (f.isAnnotationPresent(a)) {
023                    System.out.println(a.toString() + " as " + f.getDouble(null));
024                    return f.getDouble(null);
025                }
026            } catch (IllegalAccessException e) {
027                System.err.println(f.getType() + " is inaccessible for some reason");
028            }
029        }
030        return 0;
031    }
032
033    default int getInt(Class<? extends Annotation> a) {
034        for (Field f : getConstant().getFields()) {
035            try {
036                if (f.isAnnotationPresent(a)) {
037                    System.out.println(a.toString() + " as " + f.getInt(null));
038                    return f.getInt(null);
039                }
040            } catch (IllegalAccessException e) {
041                System.err.println(f.getType() + " is inaccessible for some reason");
042            }
043        }
044        return 0;
045    }
046
047    default boolean getBoolean(Class<? extends Annotation> a) {
048        for (Field f : getConstant().getFields()) {
049            try {
050                if (f.isAnnotationPresent(a)) {
051                    System.out.println(a.toString() + " as " + f.getBoolean(null));
052                    return f.getBoolean(null);
053                }
054            } catch (IllegalAccessException e) {
055                System.err.println(f.getType() + " is inaccessible for some reason");
056            }
057        }
058        return false;
059    }
060
061    default PIDCoefficients getPID(Class<? extends Annotation> a) {
062        for (Field f : getConstant().getFields()) {
063            try {
064                if (f.isAnnotationPresent(a)) {
065                    System.out.println(a.toString() + " as " + f.get(null));
066                    return (PIDCoefficients) f.get(null);
067                }
068            } catch (IllegalAccessException e) {
069                System.err.println(f.getType() + " is inaccessible for some reason");
070            }
071        }
072        return null;
073    }
074
075    default PIDFCoefficients getPIDF(Class<? extends Annotation> a) {
076        for (Field f : getConstant().getFields()) {
077            try {
078                if (f.isAnnotationPresent(a)) {
079                    System.out.println(a.toString() + " as " + f.get(null));
080                    return (PIDFCoefficients) f.get(null);
081                }
082            } catch (IllegalAccessException e) {
083                System.err.println(f.getType() + " is inaccessible for some reason");
084            }
085        }
086        return null;
087    }
088
089    @Retention(RetentionPolicy.RUNTIME)
090    @Target(ElementType.FIELD)
091    @interface TicksPerRev {}
092
093    @Retention(RetentionPolicy.RUNTIME)
094    @Target(ElementType.FIELD)
095    @interface MaxRPM {}
096
097    @Retention(RetentionPolicy.RUNTIME)
098    @Target(ElementType.FIELD)
099    @interface UseDriveEncoder {}
100
101    @Retention(RetentionPolicy.RUNTIME)
102    @Target(ElementType.FIELD)
103    @interface MotorVeloPID {}
104
105    @Retention(RetentionPolicy.RUNTIME)
106    @Target(ElementType.FIELD)
107    @interface WheelRadius {}
108
109    @Retention(RetentionPolicy.RUNTIME)
110    @Target(ElementType.FIELD)
111    @interface GearRatio {}
112
113    @Retention(RetentionPolicy.RUNTIME)
114    @Target(ElementType.FIELD)
115    @interface TrackWidth {}
116
117    @Retention(RetentionPolicy.RUNTIME)
118    @Target(ElementType.FIELD)
119    @interface KV {}
120
121    @Retention(RetentionPolicy.RUNTIME)
122    @Target(ElementType.FIELD)
123    @interface KA {}
124
125    @Retention(RetentionPolicy.RUNTIME)
126    @Target(ElementType.FIELD)
127    @interface KStatic {}
128
129    @Retention(RetentionPolicy.RUNTIME)
130    @Target(ElementType.FIELD)
131    @interface MaxVelo {}
132
133    @Retention(RetentionPolicy.RUNTIME)
134    @Target(ElementType.FIELD)
135    @interface MaxAccel {}
136
137    @Retention(RetentionPolicy.RUNTIME)
138    @Target(ElementType.FIELD)
139    @interface MaxAngleVelo {}
140
141    @Retention(RetentionPolicy.RUNTIME)
142    @Target(ElementType.FIELD)
143    @interface MaxAngleAccel {}
144
145    @Retention(RetentionPolicy.RUNTIME)
146    @Target(ElementType.FIELD)
147    @interface CrossPID {}
148
149    @Retention(RetentionPolicy.RUNTIME)
150    @Target(ElementType.FIELD)
151    @interface AxialPID {}
152
153    @Retention(RetentionPolicy.RUNTIME)
154    @Target(ElementType.FIELD)
155    @interface HeadPID {}
156
157    @Retention(RetentionPolicy.RUNTIME)
158    @Target(ElementType.FIELD)
159    @interface LateralMult {}
160
161    @Retention(RetentionPolicy.RUNTIME)
162    @Target(ElementType.FIELD)
163    @interface VXWeight {}
164
165    @Retention(RetentionPolicy.RUNTIME)
166    @Target(ElementType.FIELD)
167    @interface OmegaWeight {}
168
169    @Retention(RetentionPolicy.RUNTIME)
170    @Target(ElementType.FIELD)
171    @interface PoseLimit {}
172
173    static double encoderTicksToInches(double ticks, double rad, double rat, double rev) {
174        return rad * 2 * Math.PI * rat * ticks / rev;
175    }
176
177    static double rpmToVelocity(double rpm, double rad, double rat) {
178        return rpm * rat * 2 * Math.PI * rad / 60.0;
179    }
180
181    static double getMotorVelocityF(double ticksPerSecond) {
182        return 32767 / ticksPerSecond;
183    }
184}
